high_descs: Turn to the right and then left to face the coffee table on the left.
Pick up the remote from the right side of the coffee table.
Carry the remote and turn right, then right again to face the short side of the couch.
Place the remote on the couch, behind the blue pillow.
Turn to the right and then left to face the TV cabinet.
Pick up the remote from the left side of the cabinet.
Carry the remote and turn to the right, then right again to face the couch to the right.
Place the remote on the couch, behind the blue pillow with the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the couch.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward towards the plant, turn left into the space between the couch and table. Face the table.
Pick up the remote that's on the table.
Turn right and go forward, then turn right, step forward and turn right to face the edge of the sofa.
Place the remote on the sofa behind the blue pillow.
Step forward, turn right and go the end of the room. Step in front of the TV stand.
Pick up the remote to the left of the laptop.
Return to the edge of the sofa.
Place the remote  near the left edge and behind the blue pillow.
anns.task_desc: Find two remotes to place on the sofa.

high_descs: Turn right, walk around the coffee table, making a left to face the remote on the table.
Pick up the remote from the coffee table.
Turn right, walk around to the side of the couch.
Place the remote down on the couch by the blue pillow.
Turn right, walking to the TV console, standing in front of it.
Pick up the remote on the left of the laptop.
Turn around and walk to the couch with the blue pillow.
Set the remote down on the couch next to the other remote.
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on the couch.
